name: HigherorLower
0:
”Alexa, open higher or lower.”
”Alexa, I want to play higher or lower.”
”Alexa, start playing the game higher or lower.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: higher or lower
des: Higher or Lower is a game in which a user guesses a number between zero and one hundred, and Alexa tells the user if they need to guess higher or lower. For example if the number Alexa is thinking of is 70 and you guess 75, Alexa will tell you lower.
